install : 
1- npm i -g typescript
2- tsc -v

run :
1- tsc namefile.ts

Configuring the TypeScript Compiler
1- tsc --init


موارد مهم Configuring :
1- target : 
2- module : 
3- "rootDir": "./src",
4- "outDir": "./dist",
5- removeComments : true
6- noEmitOnError: true

Debugging:
"sourceMap": true,

file Launch.json =>      
    "preLaunchTask": "tsc: build - tsconfig.json",

any : 
1- noImplicitAny: true


function :
paramers in function : 1- noUnusedParameters: true,  
return in function   : 2- noImplicitReturns": true, 
varible in function  : 3- noUnusedLocals: true


Nullable types:
"exactOptionalPropertyTypes": true,
"strictNullChecks": true


unknown:
1- "allowUnreachableCode": true,